---
import Layout from '../../components/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Proof of works">
  <main>

    <!-- NAV -->
    <nav style="background:#143A40;padding:0 32px;display:flex;gap:0">
      <a href="/" style="padding:14px 16px;font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);text-decoration:none;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">Home</a>
      <a href="/about" style="padding:14px 16px;font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);text-decoration:none;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">About</a>
      <a href="/blog" style="padding:14px 16px;font-size:13px;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;border-bottom:2px solid #F2AA1B;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">Blog</a>
      <a href="/contact" style="padding:14px 16px;font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);text-decoration:none;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <!-- HEADER -->
    <header style="background:#143A40;padding:20px 32px;border-bottom:3px solid #F2AA1B;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px">
      <img src="/profile.jpg" alt="Victor Ong Jun Qi" style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;flex-shrink:0;border:2px solid #F2AA1B" />
      <div>
        <div style="color:#fff;font-size:18px;font-weight:700;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">Mr. Victor Ong</div>
        <div style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);font-size:12px;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">Jun Qi</div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- ARTICLE -->
    <article style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:48px 32px">

      <!-- BACK LINK -->
      <a href="/blog" style="font-size:13px;color:#143A40;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:32px;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">
        ← Back to Blog
      </a>

      <!-- META -->
      <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;margin-bottom:16px">
        <span style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:20px;background:#faeeda;color:#633806;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">Substantiation</span>
        <span style="font-size:11px;color:#888;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">April 2026 · 1 min read</span>
      </div>

      <!-- TITLE -->
      <h1 style="font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#143A40;line-height:1.3;margin:0 0 12px;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">Proof of works</h1>

      <!-- AUTHOR -->
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:16px 0;border-top:0.5px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);border-bottom:0.5px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);margin-bottom:32px">
        <img src="/profile.jpg" alt="Victor Ong Jun Qi" style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;flex-shrink:0;border:2px solid #F2AA1B" />
        <div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#143A40;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">Victor Ong</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:#888;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">14 April 2026</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- BODY -->
      <div style="font-size:15px;color:#333;line-height:1.9;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">

        <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#143A40;margin:32px 0 12px;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">Following links are proof of works I have done in the course of my role as</h2>
        <p style="margin:0 0 20px">ICT Associate.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#143A40;margin:32px 0 12px;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">Collaboration with NLB to create digital signage for Peicai Sec</h2>
        <p style="margin:0 0 20px"><a href="https://sites.google.com/moe.edu.sg/pcss-nlb">Assisted NLB and Peicai Sec to create the UI for students to browse the curated catalogue. UI is based on what is shown on NLB borrowing stations.</a></p>

        <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#143A40;margin:32px 0 12px;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">Manual HTML coding for Peicai Sec's CCAs page.</h2>
        <p style="margin:0 0 20px"><a href="https://www.peicaisec.moe.edu.sg/cca/ccas/">Pictures and links are now clickable. WYSIWYG editor in Isomer CMS is basic, hence the need for HTML coding by hands.</a></p>

        <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#143A40;margin:32px 0 12px;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">Organisation Chart for Peicai Secondary</h2>
        <p style="margin:0 0 20px"><a href="https://www.peicaisec.moe.edu.sg/our-peicai-family/staff-email-addresses-2025/">School Leaders and ICT KPs assigned me to assist with the organisation chart. I had access to the overall Org Chart in PowerPoint format, arranged by Departments to Rankings. This allows the ease of staff movements management.</a></p>

        <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#143A40;margin:32px 0 12px;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">Phototaking for Staff</h2>
        <p style="margin:0 0 20px"><a href="https://www.peicaisec.moe.edu.sg/achievements/staff/">Assisted with the phototaking of individual and group phototaking of staff from 2025 onwards.</a></p>

        <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#143A40;margin:32px 0 12px;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">Upload writeups of articles to school website</h2>
        <p style="margin:0 0 20px"><a href="https://www.peicaisec.moe.edu.sg/achievements/students-achievements/">Assisted with helping my committee members responsible for writeups, translating from Document to website formats only for Year 2025. That includes my support in phototaking for articles.</a></p>

        <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#143A40;margin:32px 0 12px;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">Academic Subject Overviews</h2>
        <p style="margin:0 0 20px"><a href="https://www.peicaisec.moe.edu.sg/academic/subject-overviews/">Rearranged each of the subjects by levels, subjects and curriculum. In Peicai, G3 is considered Express, whereas for other schools, it might be G1=Express, depending on School Leaders' decisions.</a></p>

        <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#143A40;margin:32px 0 12px;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">Articles for School Events 2025</h2>
        <p style="margin:0 0 20px"><a href="https://www.peicaisec.moe.edu.sg/school-events-2025/">Same thing, to assist my committee members responsible for writeups, translating from Document to website formats, including my support in phototaking for school events and articles.</a></p>


      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <footer style="background:#143A40;padding:16px 32px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-top:48px">
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">© 2026, Victor Ong<br>Last updated 14 Apr 2026</div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:16px">
        <a href="/" style="font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);text-decoration:none;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">Home</a>
        <a href="https://www.peicaisec.moe.edu.sg/" style="font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);text-decoration:none;font-family:'Lato',sans-serif">Peicai Secondary</a>
      </div>
    </footer>

  </main>
</Layout>
